🧠 19. Your Project-Specific Endpoint (IMPORTANT)

This is what you’ll actually use:

@app.post("/process")
def process_query(req: ChatRequest):

    query = req.message

    intent = "faq"  # placeholder
    reply = f"Answer for: {query}"

    return {
        "reply": reply,
        "intent": intent,
        "success": True,
        "response_time": 0.2
    }